<i>noun</i>: 공덕 [공덕] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>공덕 [공덕]</dt><br>
<dd>1. good deed</dd><br>
<dd>좋은 일을 하여 쌓은 업적과 훌륭한 인품.</dd><br>
<dd>Achievements and honorable character acquired by conducting good deeds.</dd><br>
<dd>2. Guna; supererogation</dd><br>
<dd>불교에서 후세에 복이 되어 돌아오는 좋은 일을 행한 덕.</dd><br>
<dd>Virtue accumulated by good deeds in Buddhism, which will return as good fortune in the afterlife.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>